        <title xml:id="spp-848-07H1-title-1"><hi rend="italics">On cutting down the old </hi>THORN<hi rend="italics"> at</hi><lb/>  MARKET-HILL. <ref target="#spp-848-07H1-footnote-title-1">1</ref><note n="1" xml:id="spp-848-07H1-footnote-title-1" place="foot">A village near the seat of Sir <hi rend="italics">Arthur Acheson</hi>, where the dean sometimes made a long visit</note></title>
